- Message search (full-text, scoped to accessible channels) — v1.0.17. Postgres
  to_tsvector('english') + GIN functional index (migration 0007); websearch_to_tsquery
  tolerates arbitrary input. GET /api/search?q=&before=&limit= scopes to the caller's
  accessible channels (accessibleChannelIDs, same rule as canAccessChannel — DMs stay
  members-only even for mods), newest-first with keyset pagination. Header 🔍 opens a
